&lt;li&gt;Identify, assess, and execute growth opportunities based on a deep analytical understanding of fan behavior, commercial drivers, and market dynamics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and apply structured problem-solving and analytical frameworks (e.g., hypothesis-driven analysis, scenario modeling) to inform strategic decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the development of&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;long-range plans and annual business strategies, ensuring alignment with League priorities and measurable outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide strategic direction for the Global Markets Program, in collaboration with Club Business Development, including:&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Defining KPIs and success metrics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MessageBody&quot;&gt;Driving structured program governance across internal central functions, local territory offices, and Clubs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
