&lt;p&gt;The Field Operations &amp;amp; Production Systems Associate plays a critical role in supporting the operational infrastructure of NFL Films’ production, event, and football operations. This position focuses on system oversight, workflow optimization, and cross‑departmental coordination to ensure smooth execution of onboarding, credentialing, hiring, and on‑location operational processes. The role also contributes directly to football operations at games and events, serving as a reliable on‑site operational resource.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position is ideal for someone who thrives in a fast‑paced, event‑driven environment and brings a systems‑minded approach to operational challenges.&lt;/p&gt;
